OL,3,CElectric HGVs being trialled across
OL,4,Cthe UK in a bid to help lorries go
OL,5,Cgreen
OL,7,FProject Jolt, led by Cambridge
OL,8,FUniversity, is working with 14 fleets
OL,9,Facross the country to explore how
OL,10,FHGV's can go green, as the deadline
OL,11,Ffor net zero approaches.
OL,13,F"The urgency of the climate crisis is
OL,14,Fdriving adoption of electric heavy
OL,15,Fgoods vehicles at a rate that few in
OL,16,Fthe industry would have expected five
OL,17,Fyears ago," said Professor David
OL,18,FCebon, Leader of Project Jolt.
