OL,3,CElectric HGVs being trialled across
OL,4,Cthe UK in a bid to help lorries go
OL,5,Cgreen
OL,7,F"But there's still a long way to go to
OL,8,Funderstand how whole fleets and
OL,9,Findustries can transition to electric
OL,10,Fheavy goods vehicles in a technically
OL,11,Ffeasible way."
OL,13,FChallenges include the cost of
OL,14,Freplacing infrastructure; the limited
OL,15,Frange of electric vehicles and the
OL,16,Flack of capacity in the national grid.
