OL,3,CElectric HGVs being trialled across
OL,4,Cthe UK in a bid to help lorries go
OL,5,Cgreen
OL,7,FNestle fills 4,000 lorries a week in
OL,8,Fthe UK - a huge operation which relies
OL,9,Fon diesel trucks, which are economical
OL,10,Fand reliable, but dirty. Which is why
OL,11,Felectric alternatives are being tested.
OL,13,FJoseph Hurst, Sustainability lead for
OL,14,FTransport at Nestle UK, says the test
OL,15,Fis highlighting some issues.
OL,17,F"We still need to get Kit Kats out
OL,18,Fexactly as we have done, but there are
OL,19,Fnew challenges from range to things we
OL,20,Fhaven't had to deal with before," he
OL,21,Ftold ITV News.
