OL,3,CElectric HGVs being trialled across
OL,4,Cthe UK in a bid to help lorries go
OL,5,Cgreen
OL,7,FProf Cebon identified charging
OL,8,Fcapacity as one of the biggest
OL,9,Fchallenges to introducing electric
OL,10,FHGV's on a bigger scale, because
OL,11,Felectrifying all lorries would require
OL,12,Fa third as much power as we currently
OL,13,Fuse across the whole country.
OL,15,F"We've got tens of thousands of
OL,16,Ffacilities like this that need to be
OL,17,Fconnected to the grid," he explained."
OL,18,FGetting a grip on that is the most
OL,19,Fimportant thing by far for the
OL,20,FGovernment to get a grip of."
