OL,3,CElectric HGVs being trialled across
OL,4,Cthe UK in a bid to help lorries go
OL,5,Cgreen
OL,7,FCost is also an issue for freight
OL,8,Foperators - an electric HGV costs
OL,9,F#300,000 upfront, while the
OL,10,Ftraditional alternative is #160,000.
OL,12,FFurthermore, an electric vehicle can
OL,13,Fcarry 18% less weight than a diesel
OL,14,Ftruck and its range can be limited to
OL,15,Faround 130 miles, which is a lot less
OL,16,Fthan the 800 mile range of a diesel
OL,17,Ftruck - although some of the fully
OL,18,Floaded trucks tested have achieved a
OL,19,Frange of over 200 miles.
